<item>
            <title>[NET-511] Exception for new SubnetUtils(&quot;0.0.0.0/0&quot;)</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/NET-511</link>
                <project id="12310487" key="NET">Commons Net</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The following example in SubnetUtils throws an exception:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;SubnetUtils utils = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; SubnetUtils(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;0.0.0.0/0&quot;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;As &apos;0.0.0.0/0&apos; is within the IPv4 specification, it should be supported.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12654194">NET-511</key>
